As if this year wasn't lit enough, house DJ and business mogul Black Coffee is set to make things even hotter with his new album set to drop the end of the year or early January. Black Coffee took to Instagram and shared a video saying he has been working on some new music and had planned to release his album soon. While he was explaining that he has been working on some music, Black Coffee revealed that he had a new song with muso Ryx. The international DJ explained that the song may be his next single. Fingers crossed it's on the new album.